snippet.title: Kitty Inu Episode 6 - KittyKart adds Genesis Kart and hazards to gameplay!
snippet.description:
The 9VRSE held a free mint for the community with 999 Genesis Karts.  Available on secondary market, Opensea, they connect to KittyKart via a MetaMask wallet and scanning the in-game QR code.  Then you can race away with a unique kart and try to avoid those hazards in the desert!

Turn up the bass on this tune "Fetish" by Trench.

#KittyInu #KittyKart #web3 #Gaming #gamefi 

www.kittyinu.com
